<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="79" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">
CHINA, Fujian Province, Ningde city, Gutian county, on the basidioma of 
<taxonomicName class="Tremellomycetes" family="Tremellaceae" genus="Tremella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Tremella fuciformis" order="Tremellales" pageId="4" pageNumber="79" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="fuciformis">Tremella fuciformis</taxonomicName>
, July 2017, X.Z. Liu (holotype strain: CGMCC 2.5724T, ex-holotype strain: CBS 15261T).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="79" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">
Basidiomaticola refers to the species isolated from the basidioma of 
<taxonomicName genus="T." lsidName="T. fuciformis" pageId="4" pageNumber="79" rank="species" species="fuciformis">T. fuciformis</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="79" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="4" pageNumber="79">
